overview: Bargain Tampa Movers is the Tampa St. Petersburg leading moving and storage company. We provide both local and long distance moves residential and commercial. Whether you move is cross town, cross country or across the globe we can help you and provide the best value in moving and storage. We know how precious your belongings are and we treat your goods like they are our own. We also handle specialty moves such as TV/Movie set moves and moves of laboratory equipment. Call for a free and quick quotation.
